<a href="https://www.reuters.com/article/us-facebook-cyber-investigation/facebook-says-hackers-did-not-use-stolen-logins-on-third-party-sites-idUSKCN1MC2S8">Reuters</a>
<a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/magazines/panache/blackberry-evolve-priced-at-rs-24990-will-be-available-on-amazon-next-week-onwards/articleshow/66052671.cms">India Times</a>,
