<a href="https://lifehacker.com/how-to-protect-yourself-after-facebooks-recent-hack-1829490273">LifeHacker</a></p>

<p><strong><font color="#0099CC">In (Cyber)Space Bots Can Hear You Speak: Breaking Audio CAPTCHAs Using OTS Speech Recognition</font></strong> <br />
Saumya Solanki, Gautam Krishnan, Varshini Sampath,  and <u>Jason Polakis</u> <br />
In Proceedings of the <a href="http://www.ai-sec.net/AISec2017/">10th ACM Workshop on Artificial Intelligence and Security (AISEC)</a>,<br />
co-located with the <a href="https://www.sigsac.org/ccs/CCS2017/">ACM Conference on Computer and Communications Security (CCS)</a><br />
